# Auto-generated GraphQL schema (NestJS).
# The backend copy IS tracked: it's the schema snapshot that CI codegen
# (axis-frontend typecheck/build) consumes. The dev server rewrites it on
# boot, so drift shows up as a diff in PRs.
schema.gql
!axis-backend/src/schema.gql

# Claude Code (ignore local state, keep shared skills + session log)
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/session-log.md
prompt.md

# Local archive (stale plans kept on disk only, not in git)
.archive/
